{
  "stem": "1413.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know what it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was just a springboard for labor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was in Kremboong from April the 2nd, 1942 till the middle of July, or end of July something.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was in July, yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, and we-- while we was there-- while we were there-- I wouldn't have thought it, even though you didn't ask me for it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I left in April 2, we didn't wear David stars yet at the time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then there come a law that you had to wear David stars.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So everybody in the camp had to sew on a David star.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] we were-- there was an order we have to go to Westerbork.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was there in April.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Left in July.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it must have been end of May or June.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Either one of the two months because I know I was there for a while.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And after that, the star was there for a while, even though when I came back, I got one day-- because my wife was sick in the hospital-- I got one day from the camp that I was-- I was in Westerbork at the time.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Yeah, that was in Westerbork.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "One day, I was allowed to go to see my sick bride in Amsterdam.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when I put on suit in Amsterdam, I left the house to go to the hospital without a David star.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I had to go back, just put a star on before I got arrested, that I wore a suit without a star.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I got married April the 1st, 1942.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And went into Kremboong April the 2nd.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "April the 2nd, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was supposed to go in April the 1st.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
